}}'''HipChat'''是一个已關閉的企業内部私人[[网络聊天|网络聊天]]和[[即時通訊|即時通訊]]网络服务。除了一对一和小组聊天外，它还具有云端文件存储、视频通话、搜索信息历史和浏览在线图片等功能。该软件可运行在[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[麥金塔|Mac]]或[[Linux|Linux]]電腦以及{{link-en|Android}}和[[IOS|IOS]]智能手机和平板电脑上<ref name="Yammer">{{Cite web|title=HipChat Is Yammer For The Masses|url=https://techcrunch.com/2009/12/14/hipchat-group-chat/|accessdate=2010-04-23|author=Kincaid|date=2009-12-14|first=Jason|publisher=[[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]]|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021072802/https://techcrunch.com/2009/12/14/hipchat-group-chat/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=HipChat: A Private IM Network for Your Team|url=https://gigaom.com/2010/04/15/hipchat-a-private-im-network-for-your-team/|accessdate=2010-04-23|author=Mackie|date=2010-04-15|first=Simon|publisher=Gigaom|archive-date=2017-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170914081522/https://gigaom.com/2010/04/15/hipchat-a-private-im-network-for-your-team/}}</ref>。自2014年起，HipChat采用免费增值模式，大部分服务為免费，一些额外的功能需要按月付费<ref name="Price">{{Cite web|title=HipChat is now free for unlimited users|url=https://blog.hipchat.com/2014/05/27/hipchat-is-now-free-for-unlimited-users/|accessdate=2014-10-28|author=Curley|date=2014-05-27|first=Pete|publisher=HipChat|archive-date=2016-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160911033316/https://blog.hipchat.com/2014/05/27/hipchat-is-now-free-for-unlimited-users/}}</ref>。HipChat于2010年推出，2012年被[[Atlassian|Atlassian]]收购<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=https://techcrunch.com/2018/07/26/atlassians-hipchat-and-stride-to-be-discontinued-with-slack-buying-up-the-ip/|title=Slack is buying, and shutting down, HipChat and Stride|work=TechCrunch|accessdate=2018-07-26|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181009041300/https://techcrunch.com/2018/07/26/atlassians-hipchat-and-stride-to-be-discontinued-with-slack-buying-up-the-ip/}}</ref>。

2018年7月，[[Slack_(軟體)|Slack]]宣佈从Atlassian手中收购HipChat的[[代码库|代码库]]和相关[[知识产权|IP]]资产，HipChat停止運行<ref>{{cite news |title=HipChat和Stride将关闭，Slack 与Atlassian握手言和 |url=https://m.thecover.cn/news_details.html?id=982619 |publisher=TechCrunch}}</ref>。此后，HipChat的客户被迁移到Slack群组协作平台，过渡期于2019年2月完成<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.cmswire.com/digital-workplace/slackatlassian-deal-marks-a-turning-point-in-team-collaboration-market/|title=Slack–Atlassian Deal Marks a Turning Point in Team Collaboration Market|work=CMSWire.com|accessdate=2018-08-01|language=en-us|archive-date=2021-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304162634/https://www.cmswire.com/digital-workplace/slackatlassian-deal-marks-a-turning-point-in-team-collaboration-market/}}</ref>。

